snippet.title: Mario Kart WII Awesome Edition Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Mario Kart Wii: Awesome Edition is a repaint-esque mod that changes the textures, music, models, and text of Mario Kart WII.

What to expect:
-Each track has their own theme, like Pizza Towers, The Mario Movie, Garfield, ETC
-Custom music with a mixture of regular video game music, shitpost music, and some from music artists
-Custom SFXs of different things to add to the insanity
-All characters being turned into either different characters, alternate variants of the characters, or just be completely cursed all together
-Custom menus with different Video FMVs and assets
-Custom models for the game's Items like the banana, the mushrooms, and the shells
-Custom text to the menus and UI
-Custom opening and ending FMVs

Gamebanana: https://gamebanana.com/mods/510399
Mega: https://mega.nz/folder/D2h3xBpS#XmQEtCUQWzLdVLIlJgYxHg
